net.proteusframework.ui.management

Class DefaultURLConfigPropertyConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.management.DefaultURLConfigPropertyConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    URLConfigPropertyConverter

    public class DefaultURLConfigPropertyConverter
extends Object
implements URLConfigPropertyConverter
    Default converter.

    This implementation supports....

    • converting entities by a serializable identifier to and from a String.
    • converting objects to strings by calling toString.
    • converting strings to numbers.
    • converting strings to Enums.
    • converting strings to Locale.
    • converting strings to Date by long or one of net.proteusframework.core.ReflectUtil#DATE_PATTERNS.
    • converting strings to any type with a String constructor or static valueOf method.

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
